[normal] communities is enshrined within the land use planning legis
[normal]lation and the industry has for
[normal] many years worked hard to be part or the local community rather apart from it. 
[normal]Many operator
[normal]s actively engage with their communities though regular open days, educa
[normal]tion initiatives and other forms of community engagements  such as site specif
[normal]ic liaison group involving loca
[normal]l elected representative
[normal]s
[normal], local re
[normal]sidents and locally based NGOs.
