[normal]e
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]organisations are working with mineral planners and industry to help nature during and after
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]minerals extraction. Together, 
[normal]they
[normal] will make substantial contributions to priority
[normal] 
[normal]habitats and species, in particular to the 
[normal]England 
[normal]Biodiversity Strategy 2020 
[normal]targets and provide richer places for people to enjoy.
